  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What the Government Statistical Service does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>The Government Statistical Service (GSS) is a community for all civil servants working in the collection, production and communication of official statistics.</p>

<p>Government Statistical Service is part of the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/civil-service">Civil Service</a>.</p>
</div>

